msgid "# Adding a custom aclnn operation"
msgstr "# 添加自定义 aclnn 算子"

msgid ""
"This document describes how to add a custom aclnn operation to vllm-ascend."
msgstr "本文档介绍如何向 vllm-ascend 添加自定义 aclnn 算子。"

msgid "## How custom aclnn operation works in vllm-ascend?"
msgstr "## 自定义 aclnn 算子在 vllm-ascend 中如何工作？"

msgid ""
"Custom aclnn operations are built and installed into "
"`vllm_ascend/cann_ops_custom` directory during the build process of vllm-"
"ascend. Then the aclnn operators are bound to `torch.ops._C_ascend` module, "
"enabling users to invoke them in vllm-ascend Python code."
msgstr ""
"自定义 aclnn 算子在 vllm-ascend 构建过程中被编译并安装到 `vllm_ascend/cann_ops_custom` "
"目录。随后，这些 aclnn 算子被绑定到 `torch.ops._C_ascend` 模块，使用户能够在 vllm-ascend 的 Python "
"代码中调用它们。"

msgid "To enable custom operations, use the following code:"
msgstr "要启用自定义算子，请使用以下代码："

msgid "## How to add a custom aclnn operation?"
msgstr "## 如何添加自定义 aclnn 算子？"

msgid ""
"- Create a new operation folder under `csrc` directory.\n"
"- Create `op_host` and `op_kernel` directories for host and kernel source code.\n"
"- Add build options in `csrc/build_aclnn.sh` for supported SOC. Note that multiple ops should be separated with `;`, i.e. `CUSTOM_OPS=\"op1;op2;op3\"`.\n"
"- Bind aclnn operators to torch.ops._C_ascend module in `csrc/torch_binding.cpp`.\n"
"- Write a meta implementation in `csrc/torch_binding_meta.cpp` for the op to be captured into the aclgraph."
msgstr ""
"- 在 `csrc` 目录下创建一个新的算子文件夹。\n"
"- 创建 `op_host` 和 `op_kernel` 目录，分别存放主机端和内核端源代码。\n"
"- 在 `csrc/build_aclnn.sh` 中为支持的 SOC 添加构建选项。注意，多个算子应使用 `;` 分隔，例如 `CUSTOM_OPS=\"op1;op2;op3\"`。\n"
"- 在 `csrc/torch_binding.cpp` 中将 aclnn 算子绑定到 torch.ops._C_ascend 模块。\n"
"- 在 `csrc/torch_binding_meta.cpp` 中为算子编写元实现，以便其能被捕获到 aclgraph 中。"

msgid ""
"After a successful build of vllm-ascend, the custom aclnn operation can be "
"invoked in Python code."
msgstr "成功构建 vllm-ascend 后，即可在 Python 代码中调用自定义 aclnn 算子。"
